This paper describes an algorithm for automatically extracting keyphrases from text, which falls under the sub-field of natural language processing (NLP). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning, which is a common technique in the sub-fields of information retrieval (IR), machine learning (LG), artificial intelligence (AI), and deep learning (DL). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which encompasses NLP and IR. The other sub-categories listed are also relevant due to the use of machine learning.
